OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FVirgin Media investigated  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover contract cancellations
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Virgin Media is being investigated by  
OL,6, the telecoms regulator over complaints 
OL,7, that it is too difficult for customers 
OL,8, to cancel their contracts.             
OL,10,FPeople told Ofcom they struggled to    
OL,11,Fspeak to a customer services agent by  
OL,12,Fphone, with some calls being dropped   
OL,13,Fand others facing long waiting times.  
OL,15,FOthers said they had to make repeated  
OL,16,Frequests to cancel their services.     
OL,18,FVirgin Media said complaints relating  
OL,19,Fto "difficulties leaving" had halved   
OL,20,Fover the past year.                    
